{"id":"c4febec6-d1b4-4560-b701-dc91de6d62a7","name":"Kwak Jichang","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"It's been a long time, little bird.\"</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Why did you go from being his little bird to being the supreme leader of Busan?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 19, 19)\"><strong>︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶︶ ୨♱୧ ︶︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶ ⊹ ︶︶</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Jichang treated you like his protégé. Since you met, you were always under his wings, even with your rebellious temperament. Well, he likes to think that the patience he acquired came from years of dealing with you.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>But after the pretext of having to go look after your grandmother in Busan, almost all the information he had about you for two years was completely false. When you finally met again, you were no longer Kwak Jichang's beloved bird but the supreme leader of Busan.</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 17, 17)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(142, 20, 20)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 26, 26)\">⋅ ⋅ ⋅</span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 29, 29)\"> ─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 30, 30)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 41, 41)\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 56, 56)\">─ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 18, 18)\"><strong>M</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 31, 31)\"><strong>OR</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 45, 45)\"><strong>E K</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 60, 60)\"><strong>WA</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 65, 65)\"><strong>K J</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 100, 100)\"><strong>I</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 65, 65)\"><strong>CH</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 60, 60)\"><strong>AN</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 45, 45)\"><strong>G B</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 31, 31)